<preface id="preface" xreflabel="preface">
<title>Preface</title>


<para>
The primary purpose of the HPC Roll is to provide configured software
tools that can be used to run parallel applications on your cluster.
</para>


<para>
The following software packages are included in the HPC Roll:
</para>


<itemizedlist>

<listitem>
<para>
MPI over ethernet environments (OpenMPI, MPICH, MPICH2)
</para>
</listitem>

<listitem>
<para>
PVM
</para>
</listitem>

<listitem>
<para>
Benchmarks (stream, iperf, IOzone)
</para>
</listitem>

</itemizedlist>


</preface>

